{"tid":2513352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★失業男\"扮工10年\"　按樓借財仔畀家用","createTime":"2021-05-02T12:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T12:32:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"37d5ec0a52e8729b89a749c0eba463f41d58860a","tid":2513352,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>銷售經理扮工10年破產 尋死前才致電求助</strong><br />\n<br />\n翁麗萍分享早前接觸到的一個求助個案，故事中的主人翁陳先生（化名）多年來任職銷售經理，年過半百卻失業，難以找到同類工作、又因自尊心而不願嘗試其他工種，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>於是他過著「10年扮工」的生活</strong></span>，直至收到一封律師信，絕望的陳先生站在西貢碼頭欲跳海輕生。或許他想在離開人世前找人傾訴心中苦，臨跳海前，他撥打了明愛財困及債務專線，告訴電話那頭的社工自己想跳海，社工叫他到明愛中心，陳先生上到中心後，只在表格填了名字便走了，「佢仲未準備好去同社工傾」。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生租住了賓館，期間社工一直致電給他跟進，終於陳先生同意再次到中心，他帶同自己的法庭文件，揭開自己扮工10年的故事。原來陳先生有一個很舊的物業，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>扮工10年仍可繼續給家用，是因為他用層樓去借「財仔」，</strong></span>面對高昂的利息，他沒錢還，直至收到收樓書，他知道一切都完了，「佢嘅物業已經無咗，已經收到收樓書，佢要點同太太仲有阿仔交代？佢面對唔到。」為免陳先生做傻事，翁麗萍稱安排了陳先生入住明愛宿舍，同時為他安排免費法律諮詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/618156/%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%B7%E6%89%AE%E5%B7%A510%E5%B9%B4-%E6%8C%89%E6%A8%93%E5%80%9F%E8%B2%A1%E4%BB%94%E7%95%80%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8-%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E6%8C%87%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E9%81%87%E8%B2%A1%E5%9B%B0%E4%B8%8D%E9%A1%98%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F618156%2F%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2589%25AE%25E5%25B7%25A510%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2580%259F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E4%25BB%2594%25E7%2595%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%259B%25B0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=e1418670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/618156/%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%B7%E6%89%AE%E5%B7%A510%E5%B9%B4-%E6%8C%89%E6%A8%93%E5%80%9F%E8%B2%A1%E4%BB%94%E7%95%80%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8-%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E6%8C%87%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E9%81%87%E8%B2%A1%E5%9B%B0%E4%B8%8D%E9%A1%98%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210429/464486891027173376739821.jpeg/knoIXXHKSz7nLxnDrrFLA8t43rS_YkI0xgPMdsYDzHY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210429%2F464486891027173376739821.jpeg%2FknoIXXHKSz7nLxnDrrFLA8t43rS_YkI0xgPMdsYDzHY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=3538fc85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd920fa12b632cb5efc10434e31e88949296287f","tid":2513352,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/145435_08be2aa0dd2179c6a2f5111a18d912fc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F145435_08be2aa0dd2179c6a2f5111a18d912fc.gif&h=b0391598&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caa0f5305ae712b06486c9c919a40524460ab43e","tid":2513352,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fa3cea7d59c97d73682a223696519a795be1a6","tid":2513352,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"黎生jpg"},{"pid":"1492d2182b168519c7cac57960943d53026d2e26","tid":2513352,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"收埋你粒星啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}